// Spec line 8: the retry counter MUST represent every value up to retry_limit.
// Equivalent combinational invariant on the comparison: an 8-bit counter can
// never equal/exceed a limit above 255, so for any reachable retry_q the give_up
// condition is unsatisfiable when retry_limit_i > 8'hFF.
assert property (@(posedge clk_i) disable iff (!rst_ni)
  (req_count >= retry_limit_i) |-> give_up_o);
